{"tid":1013074,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"嫁唔出既老女人特別麻閪煩","createTime":"2019-02-08T05:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T10:07:42.000Z","uid":156146,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c05535495331456be5af1494aca33387375e26af","tid":1013074,"uid":156146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"話說我家姐係一個快40都未拍拖既老女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直無愛情滋潤既佢成日將發火落我身上<br />\n頭先有親戚黎拜年，我地落樓下茶樓飲茶<br />\n家慈家嚴就落去攞位先，我同家姐就遲啲出門口<br />\n可能係阿媽叫家姐埋單啦<br />\n竟然話我出街做咩仲去咩飲茶<br />\n要比多份錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即時打左個凸，我飲茶出街關你撚事呀？<br />\n更何況我約人2點，食個飯又有咩問題？<br />\n態度又好撚差，又話我幫婆婆搵件外套都搵唔到，<br />\n叫我係個衣櫃搵，我答左佢好撚多次搵過無，<br />\n佢就係咁重覆叫我搵<br />\n我就大大聲話我話搵唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就發脾氣走左去<br />\n上到酒樓又黑口黑面<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打身邊有冇啲咁既老姑婆<br />\n有就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有冇辦法搞掂呢啲老處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2fa2cb2afcb5b41bf8d8160b98c937cbe2e8ce","tid":1013074,"uid":234321,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:28:08.000Z","msg":"性格咁閪點會嫁得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbad827dc5b42da2bc7a7f02b3210b5a695f0a4","tid":1013074,"uid":199162,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:28:18.000Z","msg":"正正因為性格咁閪 所以嫁唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef981c3b96d8ab65bfedade2f5c2528519b4bc96","tid":1013074,"uid":121245,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:29:43.000Z","msg":"老女人喺職場上仲閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b16e3be655eb4456d71518e678142f4f45982b8","tid":1013074,"uid":156146,"l